## Matches definition

- The 5 Bengaluru matches are hardcoded in `src/matches.js`.
- `matchId` values must be stable and safe as filenames (letters/numbers/underscore/dash).
- If match dates/venues need updating, update only `src/matches.js` and keep IDs unchanged.

